<http://example.org/film/tt0052618> a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Film>;
  <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/director> <http://example.org/person/william_wyler>;
  <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/genre> <http://example.org/movie-genre/action>, <http://example.org/movie-genre/adventure>,
    <http://example.org/movie-genre/drama>, <http://example.org/movie-genre/history>;
