<http://example.org/film/tt0296310> a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Film>;
  <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/genre> <http://example.org/movie-genre/documentary>;
  <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/productionCompany> <http://example.org/company/bbc>,
